parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the motor mounts can cause excessive engine movement, leading to premature wear on other engine components, reduced vehicle performance, and potentially causing damage to the engine or transmission.
symptoms: Excessive engine vibration
loud engine noise
engine movement or shifting
difficulty shifting gears
rough idling
decreased fuel efficiency.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, especially when the vehicle is in gear and moving.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly
often when starting from a standstill or when shifting into gear
and can reach speeds of up to 7 mph. The throttle may get stuck
causing the vehicle to lurch forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of airbags can cause distractions, injuries, and accidents, while the release of black powder can cause respiratory issues and visibility problems.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unnecessarily
airbags deploy with excessive force
airbags release black powder
airbags do not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the transmission to malfunction, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the transmission would not engage in gear
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Steering Failure in Wet Conditions
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power steering can make the vehicle difficult to maneuver, especially at low speeds, which can increase the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering system fails to assist steering
the steering wheel becomes heavy or difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to steer
especially during wet weather conditions.
